Package: scoreBPQ
Title: A package to quickly score the Body Perception Questionnaire. Takes raw data and outputs summary scores by subscale.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Logan",
           family = "Holmes",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "lgholmes@indiana.edu"),
