      person(given = "Jacek",
           family = "Kolacz",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "jkolacz@iu.edu"))
Description: This package takes raw items from the Body Perception Questionnaire and scores them according to the inputted form. Returns tScores, Percentiles, and Missing Percentage for each subscale and each observation.
